### MoneroWalletManager manual requests
# Adjust base URL if needed
@base = http://localhost:8004

### Health check
GET {{base}}/healthz

### Create a subaddress for user_id=1 (label optional)
POST {{base}}/addresses
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "user_id": 3,
  "label": "user1-main"
}

### List addresses (all)
GET {{base}}/addresses

### List addresses for user 1
GET {{base}}/addresses?user_id=5

