### Primary address
GET {{base}}/primary_address

### Sweep all from a subaddress to primary
POST {{base}}/sweep_all
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "from_address": "REPLACE_FROM_SUBADDRESS"
}

### Sweep all with explicit destination
POST {{base}}/sweep_all
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "from_address": "REPLACE_FROM_SUBADDRESS",
  "to_address": "REPLACE_PRIMARY_OR_CUSTOM"
}
